decision_details:
- the proposal made by H.E. the President in his capacity as the Minister of Highways, Ports and Shipping, to award the contracts for the widening and improvements of 5 sections of roads as given below and reconstruction of 13 bridges, in the Central and Uva Provinces as recommended by the Standing Cabinet Appointed Procurement Committee (SCAPC), was approved by the Cabinet:

* Kandy - Kirimatiya Road (0.0 - 7.64 km);
* Ampitiya - Gurudeniya Road (0.0 - 2.25 km);
* Nuwara Eliya -Ragala - Udupussallawa Road (19.0 - 46.0 km);
* Welimada - Kirklees Road (0.0 - 17.83 km); and 
* Avissawella - Hatton - Nuwara Eliya Road (98.9 - 108.49 km).
